The problem with many of the conspiracy theories that crop up after a wildl=
y successful auction is that they=E2=80=99re based on an assumption of orde=
r in the art world. =E2=80=9CThe truth,=E2=80=9D Gouzer said, =E2=80=9Cis p=
retty much chaos.=E2=80=9D It=E2=80=99s also a lot more complicated and con=
tingent. For example, the unprecedented success of the Salvator Mundi sale =
